General
=======
- Try not to exceed the 80-character "red line"

DOCUMENTATION
=============
- Use Javadoc style (at least: description (class, method), @param, @return @throws)
- Use common "tags": //TODO //FIXME //NOTE ...
- Comment code when necessary: to clarify meaning, avoid misunderstandings, ...

